{{Databox|en=Nafusi language}}'''Tanfusit''' niɣ d '''mazoɣ''' tga tutlayt lli sawaln [[Imaziɣn]] n [[Adrar n infusn|udrar n infusn]] ɣ Libya. Adrar n infusn illa ɣ tmazirt n [[Libya]]. '''Tanfusit''' tga ula yat tulayt zɣ tutlayin n imaziɣn lli ukan sul iddrn, waxxa tbidd tanbaḍt n Libya ɣ ddu ifasn l-qddafi bac ad tt tmḍl. 
Ar tt sawaln uggar n 200,000 n umdan. Tangalt -{(<nowiki>ISO 639-3</nowiki>)}- nns igat: jbn. tawjan ns Camitu-simitik zɣ tutlayin tifrusyatin niɣ d [[Tutlayin tifrusyawiyin]]. Mnct ad bdda tsmun id bu icnubcn n tutlayt mas tga zɣ tutlayin n [[tuns]]. Mac nttat naḥayat disnt.

==Adrar n infusn==
Adrar n infusn iga yan zɣ idrarn n tmazirt n [[Libya]] lli walan [[imaziɣn]] , ig yan ugadir lli bdda yakkan ixatarn n imaziɣn, inin waεrabn is iga yan udrar lli fllasn iqn. Acku midn nns gan irgazn baḥra cqqanin.

==Tirra n tanfusit== 
Infusitn ar taran tamaziɣt ns iskkiln tifinaɣ d iskkiln iɛṛabn (Ẓr tawalt ɣid: [http://www.tawalt.com/ Tawalt]) Mac ar as zmmuẓzuln zɣ mad issufɣ [[Asinag Agldan n Tussna Tamaziɣt|SGSM]] niɣ d (Asinag Ageldan Tussna Tamaziɣt) n tamazirt n [[Amṛṛuk|umṛṛuk]] iskkiln imaynutn n [[Tifinaɣ]].
